1
00:00:01,501 --> 00:00:04,295
<i>I also dreamed of having</i>
<i>a new life with you.</i>

2
00:00:04,879 --> 00:00:06,715
<i>But when I found out</i>
<i>that you were a criminal,</i>

3
00:00:06,798 --> 00:00:09,342
<i>I hid my pregnancy from you.</i>

4
00:00:09,426 --> 00:00:11,720
[HOMER]<i> You admit now</i>
<i>that Olsen is my son.</i>

5
00:00:12,387 --> 00:00:14,222
[WENDY] <i>Our son is innocent.</i>

6
00:00:15,098 --> 00:00:16,641
<i>Let him go.</i>

7
00:00:16,725 --> 00:00:19,477
[OLSEN]<i> No matter how much</i>
<i>you beg that bastard,</i>

8
00:00:19,561 --> 00:00:21,062
<i>it's useless.</i>

9
00:00:21,646 --> 00:00:24,232
- [OLSEN GROANS]
- [WENDY] <i>What are you doing?</i>

10
00:00:24,315 --> 00:00:27,527
<i>Son, this is what I've always</i>
<i>wanted for you.</i>

11
00:00:27,610 --> 00:00:29,154
<i>A better life.</i>

12
00:00:29,237 --> 00:00:31,072
<i>Together with your father.</i>

13
00:00:31,156 --> 00:00:34,284
<i>I can be a father to you.</i>
<i>I'll make it up to the both of you!</i>

14
00:00:35,326 --> 00:00:37,162
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

15
00:00:37,245 --> 00:00:41,583
- [GROANS]
- [THUDS]

16
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:43,835
<i>Enough!</i>

17
00:00:44,794 --> 00:00:46,588
<i>No one else has to die.</i>

18
00:00:46,671 --> 00:00:48,506
- [GWEN] <i>No one…</i>
<i>- </i>[GUNSHOTS]

19
00:00:48,590 --> 00:00:49,716
<i>…except the two of you.</i>

20
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:55,597
- [BOTH GRUNTING]
- [GUNSHOTS]

21
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:57,390
[OLSEN GROANS]

22
00:00:58,475 --> 00:00:59,642
[GUNSHOTS]

23
00:00:59,726 --> 00:01:00,852
<i>Mama, hide!</i>

24
00:01:01,853 --> 00:01:03,938
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

25
00:01:04,022 --> 00:01:07,067
[GROANS, GRUNTS]

26
00:01:09,444 --> 00:01:10,820
- [FLESH RIPS]
- [GRUNTS]

27
00:01:10,904 --> 00:01:15,658
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

28
00:01:15,742 --> 00:01:18,745
[CRYING]

29
00:01:20,747 --> 00:01:22,916
[GRETA SCREAMS]

30
00:01:22,999 --> 00:01:25,960
<i>My daughter!</i>
[SOBBING]

31
00:01:30,548 --> 00:01:37,514
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

32
00:01:43,603 --> 00:01:48,691
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

33
00:01:50,068 --> 00:01:51,736
[EMIL] All things considered,

34
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:53,446
you guys are lucky.

35
00:01:55,657 --> 00:01:58,576
You will all die together as a family!

36
00:01:59,953 --> 00:02:01,329
Emil…

37
00:02:03,081 --> 00:02:04,124
this is my fault.

38
00:02:04,207 --> 00:02:07,752
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

39
00:02:07,836 --> 00:02:09,379
Punish me instead.

40
00:02:09,462 --> 00:02:11,631
I wasn't faithful to my wife,

41
00:02:12,674 --> 00:02:14,676
and I failed to protect Ayen.

42
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:18,263
- [MUSIC SWELLS]
- [EMIL] <i>They were right.</i>

43
00:02:18,346 --> 00:02:22,767
<i>You're in a relationship</i>
<i>with your married boss.</i>

44
00:02:24,435 --> 00:02:27,188
<i>Pa, Magnus will help us.</i>

45
00:02:29,149 --> 00:02:33,027
<i>And Pa, Magnus and I</i>
<i>genuinely love each other.</i>

46
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:37,574
[CRYING] <i>Magnus loves me, Pa.</i>

47
00:02:39,117 --> 00:02:41,202
<i>Just let me stay here, dear.</i>

48
00:02:42,287 --> 00:02:45,623
<i>Don't fool around with that man</i>

49
00:02:45,707 --> 00:02:47,584
<i>just to get me out of here.</i>

50
00:02:47,667 --> 00:02:53,673
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

51
00:02:54,966 --> 00:02:57,677
- [MUSIC SWELLS]
- <i>Magnus and I love each other.</i>

52
00:02:59,262 --> 00:03:01,681
<i>His family already knows about us.</i>

53
00:03:03,016 --> 00:03:06,519
<i>They already do, but Magnus promised me…</i>

54
00:03:11,816 --> 00:03:16,487
<i>- Pa.</i>
<i>- Magnus better watch out when I get out.</i>

55
00:03:18,781 --> 00:03:20,325
<i>Pa…</i>

56
00:03:23,244 --> 00:03:24,913
Just kill me instead.

57
00:03:24,996 --> 00:03:26,873
Let my family go.

58
00:03:26,956 --> 00:03:29,709
None of you deserve to live!

59
00:03:29,792 --> 00:03:33,171
[TENSE, STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

60
00:03:33,254 --> 00:03:34,547
My son…

61
00:03:35,924 --> 00:03:38,134
My son is innocent.

62
00:03:38,218 --> 00:03:41,471
None of you are innocent!

63
00:03:42,347 --> 00:03:43,473
- [GUNSHOT]
- Pa!

64
00:03:43,556 --> 00:03:44,515
Enough!

65
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,808
- Enough, please!
- Magnus!

66
00:03:45,892 --> 00:03:48,436
[SCREAMS] Don't!

67
00:03:48,519 --> 00:03:50,688
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [GRUNTS]

68
00:03:50,772 --> 00:03:56,861
[TENSE STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

69
00:04:03,284 --> 00:04:04,869
[GROANS]

70
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:13,169
[GROANS]

71
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:18,299
[BOTH GRUNTING]

72
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:19,968
[BLOWS, KICKS LANDING]

73
00:04:23,721 --> 00:04:28,142
[GRUNTS, GROANS]

74
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,357
[GRUNTS]

75
00:04:36,442 --> 00:04:37,610
[SCREAMS FURIOUSLY]

76
00:04:37,694 --> 00:04:39,404
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [EMIL GROANS]

77
00:04:39,988 --> 00:04:44,701
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

78
00:04:45,285 --> 00:04:46,619
[LIAM] Ma!

79
00:04:49,956 --> 00:04:52,542
Ma! Ma! Ma?

80
00:04:52,625 --> 00:04:59,590
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

81
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:04,053
[MAGNUS GROANS]

82
00:05:04,137 --> 00:05:06,764
- Ma…
- Greta.

83
00:05:08,599 --> 00:05:10,101
Ma, please wake up.

84
00:05:11,185 --> 00:05:12,854
[CRYING]

85
00:05:12,937 --> 00:05:14,355
Wake up!

86
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,398
Ma!

87
00:05:17,817 --> 00:05:21,612
- Help! Someone help us!
- [GROANS]

88
00:05:21,696 --> 00:05:27,243
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

89
00:05:27,327 --> 00:05:31,331
Someone help us, please!

90
00:05:35,793 --> 00:05:38,504
[SOBBING]

91
00:05:40,339 --> 00:05:41,507
Ma!

92
00:05:56,773 --> 00:06:03,738
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

93
00:06:35,853 --> 00:06:42,819
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

94
00:06:57,834 --> 00:07:04,132
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

95
00:07:08,427 --> 00:07:12,557
[CRYING]

96
00:07:13,141 --> 00:07:14,475
[MAGNUS] Greta.

97
00:07:15,184 --> 00:07:16,519
I'll call…

98
00:07:16,602 --> 00:07:18,146
I'll call for help.

99
00:07:18,229 --> 00:07:24,193
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

100
00:07:24,277 --> 00:07:26,320
I'm sorry.

101
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:48,217
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

102
00:07:58,853 --> 00:08:01,314
[GROANS]

103
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:06,110
Ayen…

104
00:08:15,286 --> 00:08:17,663
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

105
00:08:17,747 --> 00:08:20,833
You've done nothing wrong, Ayen.

106
00:08:20,917 --> 00:08:22,210
Nothing.

107
00:08:23,085 --> 00:08:29,967
[CRYING]

108
00:08:30,051 --> 00:08:36,807
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

109
00:08:42,647 --> 00:08:45,066
You've done nothing wrong, Ayen.

110
00:08:47,109 --> 00:08:50,196
Magnus used you.

111
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:53,950
Greta murdered you.

112
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:57,411
I thought you were still alive.

113
00:09:00,248 --> 00:09:03,167
I kept looking for you.

114
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:07,380
I couldn't protect you.

115
00:09:07,463 --> 00:09:12,593
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

116
00:09:12,677 --> 00:09:19,642
[CRYING]

117
00:09:26,148 --> 00:09:29,986
[CRYING]

118
00:09:30,069 --> 00:09:37,034
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

119
00:09:47,753 --> 00:09:49,630
I won't give up.

120
00:09:50,798 --> 00:09:53,342
I'll continue my revenge!

121
00:09:57,221 --> 00:09:58,973
[TENSE, FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

122
00:09:59,056 --> 00:10:00,850
[GUN COCKS]

123
00:10:00,933 --> 00:10:02,268
[GROANS]

124
00:10:03,894 --> 00:10:04,979
[GROANS]

125
00:10:05,062 --> 00:10:11,402
[TENSE, FOREBODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

126
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,955
[GROANS]

127
00:10:28,461 --> 00:10:35,259
[TENSE, FOREBODING MUSIC SWELLS]

128
00:10:39,555 --> 00:10:43,225
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

129
00:10:43,309 --> 00:10:44,810
[GRUNTS]

130
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:59,867
- [DARK MUSIC PLAYING]
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

131
00:11:04,747 --> 00:11:08,751
[GRIM MUSIC PLAYING]

132
00:11:08,834 --> 00:11:10,628
[GRUNTS] Ma!

133
00:11:10,711 --> 00:11:11,879
Ma!

134
00:11:11,962 --> 00:11:13,214
[HUFFS]

135
00:11:13,297 --> 00:11:19,804
- [UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]
- [PANTING]

136
00:11:25,267 --> 00:11:27,937
- [GRUNTS]
- [GUNSHOTS, BULLETS RICOCHET]

137
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:29,271
[EMIL PANTS]

138
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:34,193
[EMIL GRUNTS IN PAIN]

139
00:11:34,276 --> 00:11:36,904
- [UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [PANTS, GRUNTS]

140
00:11:36,987 --> 00:11:41,283
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [EMIL GRUNTING]

141
00:11:41,367 --> 00:11:48,374
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [PANTING]

142
00:12:00,803 --> 00:12:02,012
[GRUNTS IN PAIN]

143
00:12:02,096 --> 00:12:04,390
[COUGHS, GRUNTS]

144
00:12:04,473 --> 00:12:10,980
["MASUNOG MAN" PLAYING]

145
00:12:14,275 --> 00:12:15,192
[DOOR SLAMS]

146
00:12:15,276 --> 00:12:19,196
[COUGHING, GRUNTING]

147
00:12:21,031 --> 00:12:22,116
Bastard.

148
00:12:22,199 --> 00:12:27,538
- [GRUNTING]
- ["MASUNOG MAN" CONTINUES]

149
00:12:27,621 --> 00:12:28,664
[GROANS SHARPLY]

150
00:12:28,747 --> 00:12:31,000
[LABORED BREATHING]

151
00:12:32,376 --> 00:12:34,336
[METAL CLANKING]

152
00:12:36,547 --> 00:12:37,798
[GRUNTS, PANTS]

153
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:44,346
- [UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

154
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:46,682
[LENI] Liam, enough. I'm begging you.

155
00:12:46,765 --> 00:12:47,933
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

156
00:12:48,017 --> 00:12:50,102
I didn't expect it to go this far.

157
00:12:50,186 --> 00:12:52,229
- [GASPS]
- I'm sorry, sir.

158
00:12:52,313 --> 00:12:54,773
I'll talk to my father.

159
00:12:54,857 --> 00:12:59,653
- [GRUNTING IN PAIN]
- [STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

160
00:12:59,737 --> 00:13:02,239
- Come with me.
- No. I'll talk to him.

161
00:13:02,323 --> 00:13:03,574
I'll beg him.

162
00:13:03,657 --> 00:13:05,201
Liam, please!

163
00:13:05,284 --> 00:13:06,577
[EMIL GRUNTS]

164
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,204
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [GROANS]

165
00:13:09,163 --> 00:13:16,128
- [DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]
- [BODY THUDS]

166
00:13:17,087 --> 00:13:18,547
[SOBS SHAKILY]

167
00:13:19,757 --> 00:13:21,926
Leni! [GASPS]

168
00:13:22,009 --> 00:13:24,303
[INHALES SHARPLY] Leni!

169
00:13:24,386 --> 00:13:27,473
[DRAMATIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

170
00:13:27,556 --> 00:13:28,641
Leni!

171
00:13:28,724 --> 00:13:32,853
- [SOBBING]
- [DRAMATIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

172
00:13:32,937 --> 00:13:34,480
[SOBS] Leni!

173
00:13:34,563 --> 00:13:36,065
[SOBBING]

174
00:13:36,649 --> 00:13:37,650
Leni!

175
00:13:37,733 --> 00:13:41,487
- [SOBBING CONTINUES]
- [SORROWFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

176
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:43,531
Leni!

177
00:13:43,614 --> 00:13:49,870
- [SOBBING CONTINUES]
- [SORROWFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

178
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:54,375
Leni! Leni…

179
00:13:54,458 --> 00:14:01,423
- [SOBBING CONTINUES]
- [SORROWFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

180
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:04,176
[SCREAMS]

181
00:14:04,260 --> 00:14:06,887
[BREATHES HEAVILY, COUGHS]

182
00:14:06,971 --> 00:14:09,306
[VOICE BREAKS] Leni, you're gone.

183
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,808
Wake up, dear.

184
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:12,726
[INHALES SHARPLY, COUGHS]

185
00:14:12,810 --> 00:14:14,436
[GRUNTING]

186
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,397
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

187
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:17,648
Leni…

188
00:14:17,731 --> 00:14:21,151
- [SOBBING CONTINUES]
- [SORROWFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

189
00:14:21,235 --> 00:14:22,111
[SNIFFLES]

190
00:14:22,194 --> 00:14:24,280
[SOBS, VOICE BREAKS]

191
00:14:24,363 --> 00:14:28,117
[GROANING IN PAIN]

192
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,785
I'll kill you, Liam.

193
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:32,121
[GRUNTS, BREATHES SHARPLY]

194
00:14:32,204 --> 00:14:33,789
[GRUNTING IN PAIN]

195
00:14:33,873 --> 00:14:35,875
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

196
00:14:37,167 --> 00:14:44,133
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

197
00:14:45,342 --> 00:14:52,099
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

198
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:59,231
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

199
00:14:59,857 --> 00:15:02,234
[GROANS, EXHALES DEEPLY]

200
00:15:03,444 --> 00:15:05,029
Ma? Ma!

201
00:15:06,864 --> 00:15:10,326
[KNOCKING ON GLASS WINDOW]

202
00:15:10,409 --> 00:15:12,453
Ma, Ma, Ma! [PANTING]

203
00:15:12,536 --> 00:15:15,164
- [GRUNTS, BREATHES HEAVILY]
- [WENDY CRIES SOFTLY]

204
00:15:15,247 --> 00:15:16,832
- You're here.
- Let's go.

205
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:18,250
[BOTH PANTING]

206
00:15:18,334 --> 00:15:20,252
Our car's stuck.

207
00:15:20,336 --> 00:15:22,379
Let's just use this van instead.
[PANTING]

208
00:15:22,463 --> 00:15:23,923
Get in. Ma, let's go.

209
00:15:24,006 --> 00:15:27,968
- [HOMER] Wendy!
- [WENDY WHIMPERS]

210
00:15:28,052 --> 00:15:29,595
- [WENDY] Olsen!
- Homer!

211
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:33,432
You may indeed be my son
because you're also a traitor!

212
00:15:33,515 --> 00:15:35,267
Let go of my mother, Homer!

213
00:15:35,351 --> 00:15:36,727
[WENDY WHIMPERS]

214
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:38,103
Fine!

215
00:15:39,396 --> 00:15:41,774
- Fine, come on.
- [WENDY WHIMPERS]

216
00:15:41,857 --> 00:15:43,734
- Let's fight.
- [WENDY] Olsen…

217
00:15:44,985 --> 00:15:47,196
The truth is, you don't owe me anything.

218
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:48,697
But your mother does!

219
00:15:48,781 --> 00:15:50,157
- [SMACK]
- [GRUNTS]

220
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:53,410
[BOTH GRUNTING]

221
00:15:54,244 --> 00:15:58,165
- [BLOWS LANDING]
- [BOTH GRUNTING]

222
00:16:13,722 --> 00:16:15,474
- [BLOWS LAND]
- [GRUNTS]

223
00:16:15,557 --> 00:16:19,186
- [LOUD THUDDING]
- [GRUNTING, GROANING]

224
00:16:19,269 --> 00:16:21,355
- [BLOWS LAND]
- [BOTH GRUNTING]

225
00:16:22,272 --> 00:16:23,482
[BOTH GRUNT]

226
00:16:23,565 --> 00:16:25,442
- [BLOW LANDS]
- [GRUNTS IN PAIN]

227
00:16:27,486 --> 00:16:28,612
[GROANING]

228
00:16:29,238 --> 00:16:31,115
- [HOMER] Take this!
- [KICKS LAND]

229
00:16:32,157 --> 00:16:34,660
- [KICK LANDS]
- [HOMER GRUNTS]

230
00:16:34,743 --> 00:16:36,120
[HOMER GROANS]

231
00:16:36,203 --> 00:16:38,580
[BOTH GRUNTING]

232
00:16:38,664 --> 00:16:40,416
- [OLSEN GRUNTS]
- [GUN CLANKS]

233
00:16:40,499 --> 00:16:43,544
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

234
00:16:43,627 --> 00:16:45,337
[SCREAMS]

235
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:49,967
[GROANING IN PAIN]

236
00:16:50,551 --> 00:16:51,802
[SCREAMS]

237
00:16:52,469 --> 00:16:53,929
[GROANS IN PAIN]

238
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:57,224
- [GUNSHOT]
- [SCREAMS, GROANS]

239
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,810
[GROANING]

240
00:16:59,893 --> 00:17:03,063
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

241
00:17:03,147 --> 00:17:04,189
Go ahead!

242
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:06,316
Shoot me dead!

243
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,277
Kill me!

244
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:10,654
Do it!

245
00:17:10,738 --> 00:17:12,406
I won't do that.

246
00:17:13,699 --> 00:17:15,242
I may be your son,

247
00:17:15,951 --> 00:17:17,703
but we are not the same!

248
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:21,498
- [BLOW LANDS]
- [OLSEN SHOUTS FURIOUSLY]

249
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:23,417
Olsen. Olsen.

250
00:17:23,959 --> 00:17:28,422
- [TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [PANTING]

251
00:17:28,505 --> 00:17:29,882
Get in the van, Ma.

252
00:17:29,965 --> 00:17:31,175
I'll find, Liam.

253
00:17:31,258 --> 00:17:32,509
I'll find him.

254
00:17:32,593 --> 00:17:35,888
- [PANTING, GRUNTS LOUDLY]
- [DOOR SLIDES OPEN]

255
00:17:38,265 --> 00:17:39,641
[DOOR SLAMS SHUT]

256
00:17:39,725 --> 00:17:46,231
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

257
00:17:48,067 --> 00:17:48,901
Liam!

258
00:17:49,693 --> 00:17:51,820
[MUSIC FADING]

259
00:18:05,042 --> 00:18:11,507
[INTRIGUING MUSIC PLAYING]

260
00:18:17,554 --> 00:18:19,932
[BAG ZIPPING]

261
00:18:20,015 --> 00:18:21,350
[UNZIPS]

262
00:18:24,812 --> 00:18:28,148
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

263
00:18:41,203 --> 00:18:43,705
<i>Who's our real enemy, Olsen?</i>

264
00:18:43,789 --> 00:18:48,794
<i>The Rojas, who take advantage</i>
<i>of the poor and the weak?</i>

265
00:18:49,628 --> 00:18:54,967
<i>Or them, who got exploited just like us?!</i>

266
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,635
<i>Your mother is right.</i>

267
00:18:56,718 --> 00:18:58,971
<i>The Rojas played all of us!</i>

268
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:02,432
<i>Will you still stand by them?</i>

269
00:19:03,183 --> 00:19:04,184
<i>Son!</i>

270
00:19:04,268 --> 00:19:08,647
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

271
00:19:08,730 --> 00:19:10,107
<i>Son,</i>

272
00:19:10,983 --> 00:19:14,069
<i>this is what I've always wanted for you.</i>

273
00:19:14,153 --> 00:19:15,988
<i>A better life.</i>

274
00:19:17,322 --> 00:19:19,658
<i>Together with your father.</i>

275
00:19:20,409 --> 00:19:22,452
<i>He's finally here right in front of you.</i>

276
00:19:24,288 --> 00:19:25,747
<i>He's finally here.</i>

277
00:19:26,248 --> 00:19:30,335
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

278
00:19:30,419 --> 00:19:34,423
[MUSIC BECOMES TENSE]

279
00:19:37,092 --> 00:19:38,594
<i>Fin, were you able to reach Olsen?</i>

280
00:19:38,677 --> 00:19:39,761
<i>Not so far.</i>

281
00:19:40,387 --> 00:19:42,472
- [GUNSHOTS]
<i>- Liam!</i>

282
00:19:42,556 --> 00:19:43,557
<i>Bro!</i>

283
00:19:44,224 --> 00:19:46,268
<i>Papa got shot! He needs help!</i>

284
00:19:51,023 --> 00:19:54,443
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [GRUNTING LOUDLY]

285
00:19:54,526 --> 00:19:57,112
<i>You took everything from me!</i>

286
00:19:57,196 --> 00:19:58,363
[SOBS]

287
00:19:58,447 --> 00:20:00,616
<i>Let's finish this once and for all!</i>

288
00:20:02,034 --> 00:20:03,285
<i>Show yourself!</i>

289
00:20:03,368 --> 00:20:07,080
[TENSE MUSIC SWELLS]

290
00:20:07,164 --> 00:20:10,626
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
